Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:59.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}注ぐ蝉時雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}追いかけてたカブトムシ
