Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要往磨刀石上洒太多水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正面七成  反面三成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天鹤之间的菜单  从梅换成竹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天藤之间的客人说料理非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:02:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还  还有  今天您的发型也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子她最近变了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  变得更加积极主动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你观察得真仔细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我去接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  这里是厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找民子有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  绪花找你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我忙不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她现在没法接
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  虽然我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是在敷衍你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.71,0:02:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周即将举办的第二十届香林祭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班要出的节目是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就决定是公主咖啡厅了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说我们班的名产的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要数两位公主了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大限度地发挥这个优势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个企划的精髓所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  有请接待小组的组长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仓结名公主～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  谢谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  理所当然地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理小组的组长是——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来民子公主～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自作主张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  公主交托给公主的灼热友情的表示！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生们就是打杂的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民你心情还不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂—  喜翠庄小队—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天送到这里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的文化祭很热闹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会像傻瓜一样闹翻天的就只有我们班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前一个学校不是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没那么欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都算是麻木的一代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}（しらけ世代：指日本战后50年代到60年代出生，对社会与政治漠不关心的青年人）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过的确  咱们班级是非常热闹的～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  这就是所谓的青春？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿青春了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民你自己不是揽下了料理小组的组长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没揽下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是大家在瞎折腾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没情调呐～机会那么难得  你也一起热闹一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  人家绪花很期待的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种期待我是敬谢不敏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还担心你会不会拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你之前说过不喜欢接待的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是工作所以没关系～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说总感觉我备受期待来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这方面上我还是非常懂得察言观色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常被别人说不懂得察言观色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  怎么那么不给面子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  星期天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用上星期五和星期六整整一天来做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期六你们两个人都得请假还真是够麻烦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我个人觉得难得一次文化祭  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我倒是继续上班也不要紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去便是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.27,0:05:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校活动就好好参加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对地  其他日子里就给我用心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这件事还得告诉小民才行  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子看起来倒不是那样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  丸谷石英先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找豆丁…助川先生是吗  请您稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电六刚才和他儿子一起出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助川现在正在外边…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儿子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我还没有决定自己到底参不参加…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然身为学生  就去开开心心玩一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期日么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要不也去逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  那天白天的预约正巧少了点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有点闲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…既然这样  如果方便的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请到我们班的咖啡厅来坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二年级A班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要是我心情好就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得小民她肯定有干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一作的标题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中女生们激昂无比的文化祭前夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会是一款佳作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是热血题材吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所说的激昂无比指的当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊熊燃烧的恋爱之火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧什么的…跟篝火似的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧的篝火和高中女生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉还是热血题材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  这样改成篝火和湿润的高中女生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要是这样的话篝火不会熄掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生  麻烦你干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜的班级要办什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀  小菜是文化祭委员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  小菜真够积极踊跃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不太擅长做这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会来帮忙的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要办什么呢  餐厅？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示一些美术作品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班里有些美术部的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位同学的作品时常会被拿到外面的展示会上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就打算以那位同学的作品为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来办一个展览之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  我一定要去看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢  整个班级的同学同心协力做一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好新鲜的感觉～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭真让人期待呢  小菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是小菜班级要展示一些画作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是一些什么样的画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民不陪我一起去看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.26,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}文化祭菜单\N{\fs28}　煮菜\N　烧烤 鱼类的料理\N　天妇罗\N　肉类的料理 盖浇饭\N　汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我鹤来民子担任料理小组组长一职
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是学校活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于要呈现给客人的料理我也不会有半点疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能做出优秀的成品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟昨天完全不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.23,0:09:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问发生了什么事…我该怎么回答呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  总之她有干劲是最好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  我们也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}（京都方言）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  难得大家做一次服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想穿一次可爱点的制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…现在做还赶不赶得上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还要花钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话说！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵锵！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是喜翠庄老式的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过老板娘  她说可以用这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  有几套拍电影的时候穿出来看过的来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那时候全都拿出来晒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有味道而且还很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有好几套  我都拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  不能搞烧烤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说不能搞  不如说难办了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在教室里是不准使用煤气的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家政教室里可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过离这里远了点  有点麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那还是把烧烤去掉的好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是鱼的味道重了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会给隔壁班添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能筹备的器材有烤盘和微波炉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是电饭煲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.04,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭的话总可以做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投蛋包饭一票  用番茄酱在饭上面写字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那样好老土见不得人的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是看中这一点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,194厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  水野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是班里大家一起决定的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后却变成这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为委员的你不也一样被硬摊上这个差事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜虫妈妈听到后就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.54,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's party
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  今天也雪愿吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这周日白天能出去一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  民子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天会晚点回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  活动是后天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后是准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我回来工作也没…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免了免了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘已经联系过公会叫人来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级团结一致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes  这是青春！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花那位在东京的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会来看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我是四十万家的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有什么男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.90,0:14:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会去交男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～好像和之前说的不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…绪花你是姓松前而不是四十万呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  这边要点菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好忙好忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  好忙好忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  变成女仆了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  来和绪花一起雪愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一起雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上要到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  刚才的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十万的女人可是为工作而活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.46,0:15:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  文化祭  努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不管什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定要做了  就要当作工作来做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些就是全部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  剩下的明天父亲会开车送来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我还是第一次看水野同学的画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起在喜翠庄工作的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说会来看的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…嗯  很厉害呢  水野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押水同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿反了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(900,330)\fs40\b1}男生{\fs56\c&H0000A8&}禁止{\r}{\b1}进入！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,SPEC2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,500)\b1}当然也{\fs36\c&H0000A8&}禁止{\r\b1}偷看！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(230,120)\fs24}小气!!\N说不能偷看\N反而更想看了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(880,40)\fs24}好想看~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.60,SPEC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1010,700)\fs28}Why？为什么？？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是菜单了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照这份菜单明天早上去购买材料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治部煮  能登牛肉盖浇饭  青鱼味噌煮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是咖啡厅  不如说是和式料理店了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  蛋包饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有加入蛋包饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学  真是惊人的合身呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  再多夸夸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么可爱是犯规的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来再来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes！大和抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的份明天会带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息会后开始练习接客的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师是喜翠庄的超级女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松前绪花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有蛋包饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  还没决定好购物的分工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.89,0:17:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要加上蛋包饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭真有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那么明天拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说是早上就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  文化祭吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大学时在电影研究会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还办了放映会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来和崇子认识也是在放映会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一不当心就直呼其名了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自己也明白要振作一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不当心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐在文化祭有什么喜欢吃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是没什么挑剔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过崇子好像说过喜欢章鱼烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在放映会上崇子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又直呼其名了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  嘘～嘘～嘘～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在情况非常不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说没蛋包饭就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  还在讨论蛋包饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听取大家的意见后由我最后决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是蛋包饭是雾人君最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做给他吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.87,0:19:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪可是从中学开始就喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我才是最喜欢雾人君的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学在修学旅行时甩了雾人君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事和这有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪可是一直忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在忍什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就说来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊  现在是在讨论料理的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成谁喜欢谁的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的料理工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不出美味的蛋包饭所以才撤下的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不同  不会被个人的感情所左右的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把工作和恋爱混淆在一起真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定要做的事  怎么能因为喜欢谁而动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.39,0:20:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是最差劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.07,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得文化祭也是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个购物的分工呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有各种准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全部都会做的  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个班级哦  大家都是团结一致的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  和我们正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一幅给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.01,0:21:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅比较好理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就挂在入口处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易理解吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,押水同学  给这幅画取个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幅画我很喜欢  但却还没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  民子公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招牌马上就做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「公主咖啡厅」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超…黏…糊糊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋包饭？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是蛋包饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.77,0:23:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}柜台内侧的厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}喔  我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对小时候的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像魔法世界一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点火了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
